  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set off on a delightful expedition and use your <strong>photographic </strong>eye to uncover the mysteries of the magical <strong>TOEM </strong>in this hand-drawn adventure game. Chat with quirky <strong>characters</strong>, solve their problems by snapping neat photos, and make your way through a relaxing landscape! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take photos with your <strong>camera</strong> to solve puzzles and help people! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/0c72d94996bdde8e54d75169079e187f.poster.avif?t=1758029984\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/0c72d94996bdde8e54d75169079e187f.webm?t=1758029984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/0c72d94996bdde8e54d75169079e187f.mp4?t=1758029984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to chill beats and take in your surroundings! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/07149042dedefe190dc9b3768408b464.poster.avif?t=1758029984\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/07149042dedefe190dc9b3768408b464.webm?t=1758029984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/07149042dedefe190dc9b3768408b464.mp4?t=1758029984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet quirky characters and help them with their problems! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/7c4b9987b01c27fb77a42ea1bbce8121.poster.avif?t=1758029984\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/7c4b9987b01c27fb77a42ea1bbce8121.webm?t=1758029984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307580/extras/7c4b9987b01c27fb77a42ea1bbce8121.mp4?t=1758029984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
